# Projects gallery

## Content schema (keep stable)

Frontmatter fields: `title`, `summary` (≤15 words), `date` / `dateEnd` (optional ISO dates), `label`, `image` (local; required to ship), `href` / `hrefLabel` (optional single link), `links` (optional `{ href, label }[]`), `order`.

- Timeline uses `YYYY` | `YYYY-MM` | `YYYY-MM-DD` strings in `index.astro`
- Project card dates: store real `Date`s; format via `formatProjectDate` (e.g. same-month range → `Apr 10–12, 2026`)
- Month precision: `YYYY-MM-01`. Year precision: `YYYY-01-01`
- No project detail pages unless asked. Image is not clickable; only the text links are
- Ship a card only with a local image **and** at least one public artifact link. Prefer study figures or title/abstract crops for publications. No hotlinks or placeholders for public cards.
## Images

- Host locally under `src/assets/projects/` — never hotlink LinkedIn/CDN (URLs expire; Astro cannot optimize remotes)
- Keep sources **uncropped**. Card shows full image with `object-fit: contain` over a blurred self-backdrop (tiny second `<Image>` + CSS blur), not a hard crop that cuts faces
- Optimize with `astro:assets` `<Image>`: WebP, quality ~80, lazy, `widths`/`sizes` matching fluid card width
- Missing image → SVG placeholder from `project-placeholder.ts` (seeded by id)

## Card UI

- Horizontal single-row scroller, full-bleed past the 38rem column
- Fluid width for **all** viewports — shared CSS vars on `.projects`, **no** hard mobile→desktop breakpoint that swaps formulas
  - `--card-width: min(20rem, 100vw - 2*pad - peek)`
- Label: solid filled accent badge, top-right over media, text uses `--accent-fg` (white/black), not accent-colored text
- Desktop/fine-pointer: prev/next chevron buttons under the scroller only when cards overflow (no visible scrollbar); touch keeps swipe + peek
- Fine-pointer hover: plain CSS lift (`translateY(-3px)`) plus a soft neutral shadow — no 3D tilt
- Fine-pointer drag-to-pan (hand cursor): `cursor: grab` / `grabbing`; `user-select: none` on the scroller for **all** fine-pointer time (not only while `.is-dragging` — selection starts in the pre-drag threshold and fights the pan); disable snap while dragging; settle to nearest card on release; suppress the click that would open a link after a real drag; leave touch on native swipe
- Order in body: date (if any) → title → summary → link(s)

## Accent (site-wide)

`--accent` / `--accent-fg` on `:root` (orange). Use for project labels, project/nav links, and timeline dots — keep one accent system, don’t invent a second palette per component.
